# Code Owners — auto-requests reviews on PR open.
#
# Even though branch protection requires 0 approvers, CODEOWNERS
# routes PRs to the right humans automatically so they at least
# get a notification when something in their domain changes.
#
# Pattern syntax: https://docs.github.com/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

